Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Radio City to close
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brl2
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Jan 1978
New York landmark and art deco 'jewel' Radio City is to close. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.